text: Sergei Diyachuk (born 4 September 1980) is a Ukrainian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Ukraine Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kremenets
